  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK253">
<l>paṭaikoṇṭār neñcampō ṉaṉṟūkkā toṉṟi</l>
<l>ṉuṭalcuvai yuṇṭār maṉam</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Like the (murderous) mind of him who carries a weapon (in his hand), the mind of him who feasts with pleasure on the body of another (creature), has no regard for goodness.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
